Functional Requirements:

system should allow the user to load BasicML program files into a UVSim
system should parse BasicML line sequentially
system should store code starting from line 00
system should get instructions starting from line 00
system should decode using the code and the opperand
code should be well organized and clear
systems should execute arithmetic expressions
systems will increment after each command
system will have a functioning read function to take instructions from user
system will be able to write to user
system will have a stop and start function
system will display contents of memory
system will write error messages
system will allow user to start and stop the program
system will handle overflow

Nonfunctional Requirements

Gui should be clearly navigable
the system should execute commands within 3 seconds or less
the system should manage overflow memory
